name: "Research Lab"

Enter: =>
    say paragraph "You are standing in a medium-sized research lab. The room is not as sterile-looking as you'd expect from a laboratory, a mix of beige walls, tan floors, and light gray counters. There's a computer with an ultrawide monitor on one of the desks that's hooked up to a bulky printer next to it. All along the walls are posters depicting laboratory safety standards and images of intricately annotated celestial bodies."
    say paragraph "Unlike the room you woke up in, you do not see any equipment out of the ordinary here. There are no crystal-powered machines and nothing resembling deliberate vandalism like you saw in the observatory dome."

